  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><p data-first-child=\"\" data-pid=\"Zc9oZybC\">性别差异在心理方面其实挺有意思的。就说说话这事儿吧，女生可能更擅长表达情感，她们喜欢分享心情，聊得细腻些，比如“我今天心情不太好，感觉被忽视了”。而男生，可能就不那么擅长直接表达情感，他们可能会说“我今天不太舒服”，然后就埋头去解决问题了。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a48a5aa0055abfd1b77871164bdc38a3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1600\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-0e189376e5650fe943ea7a337347d3e7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d76050136008ad96aebeff14d6184a88_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a48a5aa0055abfd1b77871164bdc38a3_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-a48a5aa0055abfd1b77871164bdc38a3_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"2560\" data-rawheight=\"1600\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-0e189376e5650fe943ea7a337347d3e7\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d76050136008ad96aebeff14d6184a88_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2560\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a48a5aa0055abfd1b77871164bdc38a3_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a48a5aa0055abfd1b77871164bdc38a3_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"1600\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"UcwYZ-ww\">再说说压力这事，女生可能会选择找闺蜜聊聊，倾诉一下，或者买点好吃的来调节心情。而男生可能就想着找个出口发泄一下，比如打场球、跑跑步。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e95959893c7e1b847001c01d5a8c7974_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"550\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-ed58f789b66f6075d32086312d9b7c43\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-826536f7e05a1735498d3362102830bf_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e95959893c7e1b847001c01d5a8c7974_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-e95959893c7e1b847001c01d5a8c7974_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"550\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-ed58f789b66f6075d32086312d9b7c43\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-826536f7e05a1735498d3362102830bf_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e95959893c7e1b847001c01d5a8c7974_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e95959893c7e1b847001c01d5a8c7974_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"550\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"NVv23BjP\">还有，男生可能在处理问题时更偏向逻辑和理性，比如“这个问题，我们应该这样解决”。而女生可能会考虑更多人的感受，比如“我们这样做，会不会伤害到别人呢？”</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9fa46274d091ea699e9bbcf0b028b71_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"2000\" data-rawheight=\"1276\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-df47186d57973346645cecaa589ea488\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2efab699296f475000f694cd73c418b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"2000\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-a9fa46274d091ea699e9bbcf0b028b71_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-a9fa46274d091ea699e9bbcf0b028b71_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-rawwidth=\"2000\" data-rawheight=\"1276\" data-size=\"normal\" data-original-token=\"v2-df47186d57973346645cecaa589ea488\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-c2efab699296f475000f694cd73c418b_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"2000\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-a9fa46274d091ea699e9bbcf0b028b71_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-a9fa46274d091ea699e9bbcf0b028b71_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"1276\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"Zc7WIoac\">当然，这些差异也不是绝对的，每个人都有自己独特的性格和方式。而且，现在社会也越来越注重性别平等，男女之间的差异也在逐渐缩小。</p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
